Package: twhotel
Title: Taiwan Tourist-Hotel Monthly Operating Statistics as Panel Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yuyou", "Liou", email = "yuyou.liou@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Scrapes the Taiwan Tourism Administration "Tourist Hotel Operating
    Statistics" (觀光旅館營運統計) file listing, downloads the monthly XLSX
    reports, parses the per-hotel operations and guest tables, and combines them
    into a tidy hotel-by-month panel dataset for empirical analysis. The source
    listing is at
    <https://admin.taiwan.net.tw/businessinfo/FilePage?a=10425>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    dplyr,
    httr2,
    readr,
    readxl,
    rvest,
    stringr,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
URL: https://github.com/yyliou/hotel
BugReports: https://github.com/yyliou/hotel/issues
